504	84	A.14.2.4	Restrictions on changes to software packages	Restrictions on changes to software packages	Beperkingen op wijzigingen aan softwarepakketten	Modifications to software packages should be discouraged, limited to necessary changes and all changes should be strictly controlled.	Modifications to software packages should be discouraged, limited to necessary changes and all changes should be strictly controlled.	Wijzigingen aan softwarepakketten behoren te worden ontraden, beperkt tot noodzakelijke veranderingen en alle veranderingen behoren strikt te worden gecontroleerd.	250
505	85	A.14.2.5	Secure system engineering principles	Secure system engineering principles	Principes voor engineering van beveiligde systemen	Principles for engineering secure systems should be established, documented, maintained and applied to any information system implementation efforts.	Principles for engineering secure systems should be established, documented, maintained and applied to any information system implementation efforts.	Principes voor de engineering van beveiligde systemen behoren te worden vastgesteld, gedocumenteerd, onderhouden en toegepast voor alle verrichtingen betreffende het implementeren van informatiesystemen.	250
506	86	A.14.2.6	Secure development environment	Secure development environment	Beveiligde ontwikkelomgeving	Organizations should establish and appropriately protect secure development environments for system development and integration efforts that cover the entire system development lifecycle.	Organizations should establish and appropriately protect secure development environments for system development and integration efforts that cover the entire system development lifecycle.	Organisaties behoren beveiligde ontwikkelomgevingen vast te stellen en passend te beveiligen voor verrichtingen op het gebied van systeemontwikkeling en integratie, die betrekking hebben op de gehele levenscyclus van de systeemontwikkeling.	250
